Description:
Describing Amec Foster Wheeler? Excellence in delivery, a highly-integrated and people oriented business, producing high-value solutions for our customers. 

We are 40,000 exceptionally talented people throughout our global operations;
150+ years of history, operating in over 50 countries. We serve the oil & gas, clean energy, environment & infrastructure and mining markets. Across these markets, we offer consultancy, engineering, project management, operations and construction services, project delivery and specialised power equipment services to our customers worldwide.

Although the world has dramatically changed since our story began in 1955 when our founder Jack E. Caveney invented the Panduct wiring duct in his garage, our spirit of discovery and can-do attitude have remained. Choosing to innovate rather than imitate, we continue to create leading-edge physical electrical and network infrastructure solutions across a wide spectrum of business environments.

As a customer-focused company, we pride ourselves on creating a continuous flow of new products, software, and solutions designed to help companies achieve their business goals.&nbsp;

We understand that everyone’s challenges are unique, which is why we offer an extensive product portfolio to help our customers achieve and exceed their operational and financial goals. From data centers and office facilities to plant floors and processing lines, we design, build, install, and service innovative solutions that turn connectivity into a competitive advantage.
